reviews.reviewText: Everything comes in a plastic case to keep them in for next time you need one. Comes with directions and a QR code to watch a video on the directions. It also comes with screen cleaning cloth and tabs to help you line up the screen protector. The tabs did not really help but I used the camera hole at the top to help line it up and it worked the first time.I have had it on my phone for a few weeks and have dropped it multiple times with no damage.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great product. Even greater customer service.
reviews.reviewText: Original review: I applied the screen protector to my phone shortly after delivery. First piece of glass went on smoothly, but immediately I noticed a notch on the left side of the glass causing what looked to be a piece of dust refracting light around it. Upon further inspection, it was a slight, but enough, notch to cause the refracted light.No big deal. It's a 3 pack. I removed the glass, confirmed the notch, then put a second piece on, and lo and behold, the same thing. This time just further up the same side.It would appear the manufacturing process used here is causing this. Maybe these just slipped through quality control. Frustrated, I repacked the first piece, inspected the third confirming a slight notch on it as well, and left the second one on bc my phone should, for now, be protected. It's hardly an eye sore, but one nonetheless.I am strongly considering returning this product bc of this. I have always done well applying screen protectors to my phones and am 100% certain of the issue and it's origin here.Hoping to get a response and proper resolution from Supershieldz.**Please note that these are not chips or cracks in the protectors that I am referring to. These are normal cuts made when making each protector from a much bigger piece of material, in this case 9H tempered glass. This 3 pack, and I assume others, just didn't come out as smooth causing the refracted light on the left edge, possibly confirming the place where each cut was made. Typically, these cuts are rendered non-existent by the end of manufacturing. Not in this case.UPDATE: Customer service quickly responded and without hesitation sent me a replacement 3 pack and the pieces in that set were perfect. The one I applied fit perfectly and looked like it came on the phone to begin with. Happy customer all around!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very good protection
reviews.reviewText: I've been using Supershieldz for a few years now and have been very satisfied. Since this recent purchase is for my new phone, it hasn't ben "tested" (thank God). Shortly after purchasing my previous phone, I dropped it on a gravel road, it landed screen side down. The screen was shattered. I was sure that when I took the Supersheilz protector off, the phone's screen would have been cracked. I was VERY surprised and happy to see that the phone's screen was still intact. I doubt that the older flexible-style screen protectors would have done as good a job.Definitely a worthwhile investment for your new phone.
